{"tid":492685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[腦魔加人工] 綜援生果金明年擬加1.4%","createTime":"2017-12-07T19:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T19:03:13.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"afea78b9965fdad6696a7da4481f0f6d09141ffd","tid":492685,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T19:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171207/large/1512654077_b2ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171207%2Flarge%2F1512654077_b2ff.jpg&h=4e6332cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局提交立法會財委會的文件透露，當局建議將綜援、俗稱「生果金」的高齡津貼、長者生活津貼，以及傷殘津貼等公共福利金額，明年2月1日起再調高1.4%至1.5%，預計每年會增加6.3億元的經常開支。<br />\n<br />\n新金額調整後，<span style=\"color: red;\">單身成人的綜緩受助金額，會由目前的2,420元，增加至2,455元</span>；長者的綜緩受助金額則由3,435元，增至3,485元；生果金亦會由1,325元，增加至1,345元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加左35蚊"}]}